values: These Mariani Vanilla-Flavored Yogurt Raisins are an ideal snack to grab when your sweet tooth beckons. They are made with fresh, sun-ripened fruits dipped in creamy goodness. These tasty morsels are gluten-free and a delicious treat for the whole family to enjoy, especially for those that are always on-the-go. They are available in a convenient 8 oz size resealable bag. These Mariani dried fruit raisins bring healthy and satisfying together with ease. They are a high-energy snack that offers 8 percent of the daily value of vitamin D per serving.
